data.description: Step into a home that radiates warmth and brightness, thanks to its custom woodwork and fresh paint throughout. The main floor is a haven with a personalized built-in bookcase, a fireplace wrapped in wooden accents, and a dining area featuring a beautifully adorned ceiling. Enjoy a mix of delightful ceramic tiles and warm wood floors underfoot.  The kitchen has granite countertops and walnut cabinets. Venture upstairs to discover 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, with one room transformed into a spacious master closet. Uncover an additional unpermitted room in the garage.  Situated in a convenient location, this home is a heartbeat away from amenities, schools, and the allure of local wineries.
